com.gfycat.core.contentmanagement

Interface UserOwnedContentManager


  • public interface UserOwnedContentManager
    Allows User owned Gfycats management.

    User owned Gfycats are the ones with Gfycat.getUserName() equal to UserInfo.getUserid().
